Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.25,0:01:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海龍的頭目朱羅\N被手下銀丈背叛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.49,0:01:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陷入絕對的危機中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.66,0:01:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心為了救朱羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.03,0:01:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到掉入瀑布的深潭中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.34,0:02:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十七話\N燃燒的戰慄之島！\N真紅的海盜完結篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.85,0:02:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想親手來收拾他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.85,0:02:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常的遺憾\N從這麼高的地方掉下去沒救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.82,0:02:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅這樣就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.52,0:02:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是屍體不能浮起來的瀑布深潭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.50,0:02:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不去確認屍體就沒辦法安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.43,0:02:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們去查看一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.73,0:02:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.26,0:02:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行…不早點處理不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.40,0:03:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.18,0:03:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腳的子彈不快點\N取出來的話會爛掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.72,0:03:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是你隱密的家嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.39,0:03:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干的…有乾淨的布嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.23,0:03:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有去幫我燒熱水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.43,0:03:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.64,0:03:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.48,0:03:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手術！…小生…可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.85,0:03:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐  你還活著嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.72,0:04:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼可以死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.49,0:04:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是來救劍心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了  大家都沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.43,0:04:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡  這些傢伙\N竟然讓船爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.34,0:04:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我遇到這種事\N我絕對不會原諒他們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.31,0:04:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了\N這麼有精神就沒關繫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.75,0:04:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁那些傢伙還沒發現前\N快到島上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.42,0:05:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣應該可以了…\N處理得不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.62,0:05:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托你的福辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.06,0:05:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去會感冒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.79,0:05:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有換洗的衣服…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.63,0:05:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.24,0:05:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不簡單…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼都準備齊全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.91,0:05:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這真是太好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.82,0:05:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.42,0:06:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐  你要做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.09,0:06:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放  放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.03,0:06:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以尋死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.80,0:06:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有領導海龍的能力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.87,0:06:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣活下去太丟臉了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如早點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.54,0:06:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確\N朱羅小姐沒有做頭目的資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.45,0:06:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有相信朱羅小姐的夥伴在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猿次郎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.86,0:06:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣你還要不管他\N而自私的尋死嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.99,0:06:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海龍的頭目只有這樣的程度嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.97,0:06:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給貧窮的孩子們生存的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.20,0:07:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是你的父親嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.61,0:07:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生所相信的朱羅小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.94,0:07:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使陷入絕望也會往前看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.01,0:07:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是這樣的一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.39,0:07:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這真是非常的失禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧  我已經不會死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.26,0:07:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.47,0:07:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是你做的嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.11,0:07:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們找到了換洗的衣服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.58,0:07:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鮮艷的粉紅色…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.88,0:07:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常的適合朱羅小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.68,0:07:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,濕的衣服對身體不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.77,0:08:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好嗎  朱羅記著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.07,0:08:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們海龍\N是為了脫離貧苦生活而戰鬥的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.71,0:08:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們必須給飢餓漁夫的孩子當天的食物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.68,0:08:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…再怎麼的\N從不正當的船裏搶錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.68,0:08:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,略奪是一種卑劣的行為\N這…是改不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.76,0:08:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真正的夢想\N是能引以為傲的生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.66,0:08:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要去搶奪任何人\N不要去束縛任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.20,0:08:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能自由自在的在海裏生活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.83,0:08:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼時候給你祝福時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.07,0:08:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就要想起今天所說過的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.71,0:08:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也會有喜歡的男人出現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.04,0:08:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時你就跟著那男人\N率領海龍實現我的夢想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.78,0:08:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巖藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.05,0:08:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你死去母親的衣服…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼時候有喜歡的男人\N就穿著它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候我會給你祝福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.00,0:09:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我打扮成女孩的樣子\N我絕對不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.56,0:09:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅跟那混蛋的屍體\N還沒有浮上來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.16,0:09:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然他們都葬身瀑布的深潭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.47,0:09:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要讓你看一件好玩的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.60,0:09:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.31,0:09:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是巖藏老頭子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.08,0:09:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們對他做了什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.98,0:09:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他吞這東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鴉片…嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.15,0:10:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千本屋先生啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.99,0:10:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟這寶物真是威力無窮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.39,0:10:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經覺悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.60,0:10:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你們合作做到底了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.03,0:10:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是很好的覺悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.57,0:10:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，把那老頭子關到倉庫去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.70,0:10:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀丈  慶祝宴已經準備妥當了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.34,0:10:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀丈  從今天開始\N你就是我們的頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.41,0:10:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了  大家好好慶祝一番吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.46,0:10:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.69,0:10:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也去祝福銀丈老大吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.30,0:10:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以喝到明天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.97,0:11:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼時候你有喜歡的男人\N就穿這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.15,0:11:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐…很適合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.65,0:11:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村！我.我怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.42,0:11:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猿次郎…巖藏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱…朱羅小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.89,0:11:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巖藏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底發生了什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.00,0:11:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼一回事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.40,0:11:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀丈那傢伙…\N和千本屋合作…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.34,0:11:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀丈嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鴉…鴉片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.64,0:11:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.91,0:11:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巖藏…他們不會\N讓你吞了鴉片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.41,0:11:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱…朱羅小姐…快逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.52,0:11:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀.銀丈這傢伙\N我不會原諒你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.76,0:11:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這條船把朱羅小姐從這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.60,0:11:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點讓大夫看是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.94,0:12:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.61,0:12:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那老人…的樣子好像不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像讓他吞了鴉片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.11,0:12:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快把他帶到醫生那裏去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.31,0:12:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要把船開出去\N我們到那裏去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.55,0:12:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猿次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.76,0:12:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老人家  不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.89,0:12:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.40,0:12:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐  你做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.60,0:12:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去跟銀丈一決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.31,0:12:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你用那條船離開這裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.18,0:12:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村  這是你的刀還給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.45,0:12:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們二人…拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.52,0:12:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.73,0:13:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總算到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真討厭  和服好重喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心在哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.77,0:13:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.34,0:13:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒聽到什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.01,0:13:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.24,0:13:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼？在舉行祭典嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.08,0:13:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在森林的那邊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.68,0:13:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.98,0:13:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許劍心會在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.55,0:13:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼各位兄弟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.29,0:13:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們來為新的頭目\N銀丈老大來祝慶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.30,0:13:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家盡情的喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.61,0:13:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿…恭喜你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.08,0:13:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有鴉片和彈藥\N我什麼都可以做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.58,0:13:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是在這宴會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還想要有一個餘興節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.19,0:13:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,餘興？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.35,0:13:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅那小子…\N那小姑娘還活著的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.92,0:14:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要把她放入火中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.83,0:14:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果還活著\N我想讓她看一看地獄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.83,0:14:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死了就沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.97,0:14:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.08,0:14:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱囉！你還活著嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.65,0:14:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開  我沒工夫找\N你們這些小嘍嘍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.92,0:14:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你破壞約定而運送鴉片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.29,0:14:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使你連骨髓都腐敗的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.66,0:14:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由我朱羅來負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.39,0:14:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀丈  我要把你打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.63,0:14:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結束海龍\N這是海龍的首領最後的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.33,0:14:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.57,0:14:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太有趣了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.54,0:14:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要打倒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.31,0:14:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.91,0:14:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還想要\N把你丟到火裏去燒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.18,0:14:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這真是飛蛾撲火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.05,0:15:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要鬼扯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.62,0:15:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村  是你給我戰鬥的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.76,0:15:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種眼神我也回給你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀丈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.61,0:15:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這女人去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等  等一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.37,0:15:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我輸了  我已經不再反抗你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.04,0:15:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.30,0:15:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.31,0:16:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是銀丈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.55,0:16:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.05,0:16:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過了  不管手再怎麼髒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.25,0:16:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迅速向上爬的人就是勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.42,0:16:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後笑的是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.29,0:16:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我瞧不起你這魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.70,0:16:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.87,0:16:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還活著嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.60,0:16:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀丈\N我不能再讓你橫行霸道下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.01,0:16:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐的遺憾\N由我來替她找回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.53,0:16:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.60,0:16:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.24,0:17:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由我來對付你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.75,0:17:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.42,0:17:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流！龍槌閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.63,0:17:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀丈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.60,0:17:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.57,0:17:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.87,0:17:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐  不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.87,0:17:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個混蛋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.58,0:17:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看吧  用這個把那混蛋\N炸得粉身碎骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.98,0:17:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手  這樣會引爆其他的炸藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,整個村子都會被毀掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.96,0:17:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.24,0:18:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這太厲害了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.08,0:18:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心不會也在裏面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.08,0:18:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.85,0:18:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.75,0:18:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.72,0:18:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.46,0:18:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.12,0:18:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.39,0:18:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.23,0:18:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.13,0:18:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊吧  劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.63,0:18:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生沒什麼的  只是朱羅小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.50,0:18:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作一點朱羅小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.30,0:18:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你救過我的命\N現在輪到我救你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.21,0:18:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.24,0:18:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有時間慢吞吞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.63,0:19:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好大的火\N這樣燒下去島也會消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.14,0:19:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海盜的島也完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.49,0:19:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思  緋村…\N讓你幫了很多次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.40,0:19:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,互相吧…那麼朱羅小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.60,0:19:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從現在起有什麼打算呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.00,0:19:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在還沒…\N一下子發生太多事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.91,0:19:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能瞭解…\N因為什麼都失去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.94,0:19:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.51,0:19:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好大…這是伊勢龍蝦嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.85,0:20:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到有這麼大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.12,0:20:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐還剩下最重要的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.59,0:20:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼時候我會實行…\N父親沒辦法實現的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.66,0:20:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不從任何人那裏奪取東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.50,0:20:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不被任何人所束縛\N在海裏自由自在的生存…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.97,0:20:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親的理想王國…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.23,0:20:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是朱羅小姐的話\N一定能實現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.67,0:20:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家要不要到我家來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.91,0:20:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先好好休息一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.24,0:20:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能這樣  我們可是通緝犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.05,0:20:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.98,0:20:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.68,0:20:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村  你有很好的夥伴在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.55,0:20:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.29,0:20:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巖藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.06,0:20:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.92,0:20:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們出海吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.39,0:20:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陸地上太無聊了\N沒辦法再待下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.46,0:20:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你什麼時候說過了\N想要以朋友來跟我認識…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.04,0:20:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次再見面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.67,0:20:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼時候…什麼地方…\N以朋友的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.75,0:21:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.75,0:21:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.67,0:23:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕府後10年…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.61,0:23:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們公敵的美男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.21,0:23:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出現在明治的東京了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.95,0:23:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.89,0:23:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浪客劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.69,0:23:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新血戰的序曲\N逼近而來的狼的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.79,0:23:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個陷阱\N從齊藤開始露出獠牙來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.59,0:23:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再度的襲向劍心

